Interface IEndDate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MonthlyDonation, Pledge
    public interface IEndDate
    Interface providing the ability to check the validity of submitted ending dates (cancellation and processing dates) of donations, in relation to their creation.

                      Donation donation)
               throws InvalidDateException
        Ensures the cancellation date of a monthly or processing date of a pledge cannot be set prior to the creation date.
